*** Story***

Once upon a time , in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree,
which was on the bank of the river.In the same forest river lived the Crocodiles and croc wifes.
The monkey is a kind hearted fellow , who helps everybody but the croc is cunning. The croc met the moneky and said its starving and monkey offered some fruits to it and said he would wait in the  banks of river to feed the croc family every day.
